quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  25,44,“Kapena ukuganiza kuti ambiri a iwo akumva kapena kuzindikira? Iwo sali kanthu kena koma ali ngati ziweto. Ndipo iwo asokera kwambiri njira
  25,45,"“Kodi sudaone momwe Mbuye wako wautambasulira mthunzi? Akadafuna, akadauchita kuti ukhale wokhazikika (wosasinthasintha). Ndipo talichita dzuwa kukhala chisonyezo chake"
  25,46,“Kenaka tikuufumbata kwa Ife m’kufumbata kwapang’onopang’ono (kufikira wonse wutachoka)
  25,47,"“Ndipo Iye ndi amene wakuchitirani usiku kukhala monga chovala, ndipo tulo monga mpumulo, ndipo usana wauchita kukhala monga nthawi youka (kuimfa)"
  25,48,"“Iye ndi Yemwe amatumiza mphepo kukhala nkhani yabwino patsogolo pa chifundo chake (mvula), ndipo kuchokera kumitambo tikutsitsa madzi oyera"
  25,49,"“Kuti ndi madziwo tiukitse dziko lakufa (lachilala), ndikumwetsa zina mwa zimene tidazilenga monga ziweto ndi anthu ochuluka"
  25,50,"“Ndiponso ndithu tikuigawa (mvulayi) pakati pawo kuti akumbukire, ndipo anthu ambiri akukana (kuthokoza Allah) koma kupitiriza kusakhulupirira"
  25,51,"“Ndipo tikadafuna, tikadatuma mchenjezi wawowawo m’mudzi uliwonse, (koma tatuma Muhammad {s.a.w} kuti akhale mchenjezi wa onse"
  25,52,“Choncho usawamvere osakhulupirira koma limbana nawo ndi iyo (Qur’an); kulimbana kwakukulu
  25,53,"“Ndipo Iye (Allah) ndi Yemwe wazikumanitsa nyanja ziwiri, iyi yamadzi okoma othetsa ludzu ndi iyi yamadzi amchere owawa. Ndipo waika malire ndi chitsekerezo chotsekereza pakati pa izo"
  25,54,“Ndipo Iye ndiye adalenga munthu ndi madzi ndiponso adamchitira chibale cha magazi ndi chibale cha ukwati. Ndipo Mbuye wako ali Wokhoza chilichonse
  25,55,"“Ndipo (ena mwa anthu) akupembedza zina zake kusiya Allah, zomwe sizingawathandize ndiponso sizingawadzetsere masautso (atasiya kuzipembedza). Ndipo wosakhulupirira ndi mthandizi wa zoipa poukira Mbuye wake"